-- Conergy Chief Executive Sees Operating Margin of At Least 20%
-- B y   S t e f a n   N i c o l a
-- 2012-04-16T08:46:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-16/conergy-chief-executive-sees-operating-margin-of-at-least-20-.html
Conergy AG (CGYK)  Chief Executive Officer
Philip Comberg said today that the German solar-panel maker
expects an operating margin of at least 20 percent in the first
quarter. Comberg made the comments citing preliminary figures in
an e-mailed statement to Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Nicola in Berlin at 
 snicola2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
